Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with image fusion techniques and quality assessment, which falls under the domain of computer vision. 
2. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper involves the processing and manipulation of satellite images, which can be considered as a sub-domain of computer graphics. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper may involve techniques for retrieving information from satellite images, such as object detection or classification. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the fusion of different types of images, which can be considered as a multimedia processing task. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper may involve the use of machine learning or other AI techniques for image fusion and quality assessment.
